cast.overview: A young girl discovers a secret map to the dreamworld of Slumberland, and with the help of an eccentric outlaw, she traverses dreams and flees nightmares, with the hope that she will be able to see her late father again.
cast.title: Slumberland

details.biography: Ava Cheung is a Canadian actress who at a young age realized her love for the performing arts. After years of extensive dance training and experience, Ava was approached by a Toronto agent to venture into the world of film and television. She is best known for her roles as Lucy Hubble in Reacher and a young La'an Noonien-Singh in the Star Trek: Strange New Worlds.
details.name: Ava Cheung
